Beautiful 4 bedroom 2.5 bath home in Forest Hills School district. This home is a great place to settle in Anderson township with walking access to Nagel Middle School, large 2 car garage, and spacious yard including a small basketball court, and a finished basement with home theater. Great home for your family to settle and for entertaining!<br>
<br>
Home will be updated with new carpet before tenant takes occupancy. <br>
<br>
Available for rent Late August.<br>
<br>
FEATURES<br>
Sq Footage: 2030 sqft.<br>
Bedrooms: 4<br>
Bathrooms: 2.5<br>
